{"tid":611834,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"二戰 點解當時日本唔聯同德國東西夾攻蘇聯?","createTime":"2018-03-31T12:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T08:48:26.000Z","uid":155883,"like":8,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3540f45b4c0fac47198069955e7c7c0606bcd8ee","tid":611834,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:11:18.000Z","msg":"德國單挑蘇聯已經打到莫斯科, <br />\n日本陸軍/空海都係出哂名<br />\n而且地理上日本又係鄰近蘇聯<br />\n加上中國東北一早比日本佔據哂, 擺哂重軍係到<br />\n如果東西方一齊夾擊蘇聯, 絕對可以收史太林皮<br />\n鄰近既中國當時仲打緊內戰<br />\n唔會有時間幫手, 而且 日本/中國軍力差太遠<br />\n根本幫唔到<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以解答下??"},{"pid":"748254eb83037729c0300a74c7e5ff4389fa7815","tid":611834,"uid":138790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:12:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AB%BE%E9%96%80%E7%BD%95%E6%88%B0%E5%BD%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25AB%25BE%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%25BD%2595%25E6%2588%25B0%25E5%25BD%25B9&d=y4chBs1IqmZRMRvYqKKP0NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=8d58ed13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AB%BE%E9%96%80%E7%BD%95%E6%88%B0%E5%BD%B9</a>"},{"pid":"abda9914638c14f56b4e810317ab289ca23f8022","tid":611834,"uid":144664,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:18:03.000Z","msg":"其實日本有試過係蒙古滿洲邊境同蘇聯打<br />\n空軍佔優但陸軍比紅軍秒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即刻簽互不侵犯條約唔敢打 北方戰略失敗所以先要轉移重心向南發展打印度支那同東南亞 <br />\n巴巴羅薩之際 希特拉有叫過日本一齊打但佢地堅決拒絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為唔想面對蘇聯東方陸軍同（有機會）西伯利亞駐軍"},{"pid":"1ba23e0ed9fd06c6b8b89dcd8ca7221d3cb0d19f","tid":611834,"uid":155883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"748254eb83037729c0300a74c7e5ff4389fa7815","tid":611834,"uid":138790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T12:12:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AB%BE%E9%96%80%E7%BD%95%E6%88%B0%E5%BD%B9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.